<b>Collector</b><br />
This is a quarantine mailbox with some features.<br />
With one single mailbox created on your real email server you can:<br />
<li> Catch all junk emails.</li>
<li> Receive detailed reporting emails for each spam or virus email.</li>
<li> Receive spam sent to Traps.</li>
<li> Helps Scrollout F1 to learn from spam & legit emails using IMAP service.</li>
<li> Whitelist sender domain using drag & drop emails (with MS Outlook)</li>
<li> Blacklist sender address using drag & drop emails (with MS Outlook)</li>
<li> Manage everything using an IMAP clients (as Outlook)</li>